title: BLACK+DECKER 60V MAX* POWERBOOST Cordless Blower (LSW60C)
description: Clear leaves and lawn debris quickly and thoroughly with this powerful 400 CFM leaf blower. When you run into stubborn debris, get a boost of extra power with the push of a button, or use the built-in metal scraper to loosen things up. There’s even a built-in state of charge indicator, so you always know how much power you have left.
